<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Thanks for selecting Depstar.com, <%= @shipping_detail.first_name %></h1>

	<div class="conditions">		
		<h3><%= @shipping_detail.product.name %></h3>
		
		<h4>Amount you will receive: <%=  number_to_currency(@shipping_detail.question_response.quote) %>
		
		<% if @shipping_detail.product.try(:question_1_is_enabled) %>
			<p>
				<b><%= @shipping_detail.product.question_1_name %> </b> <br/>
				<%= radio_button_tag('question_response1', 'question_1', (@shipping_detail.question_response.question_1 == "True" ? true : false), :disabled => true) %> Yes
				<%= radio_button_tag('question_response1', 'question_1', (@shipping_detail.question_response.question_1 == "True" ? false : true), :disabled => true) %> No
			</p>
		<% end %>

		<% if @shipping_detail.product.try(:question_2_is_enabled) %>
			<p>
				<b><%= @shipping_detail.product.question_2_name %> </b> <br/>
				<%= radio_button_tag('question_response2', 'question_2', (@shipping_detail.question_response.question_2 == "True" ? true : false), :disabled => true) %> Yes
				<%= radio_button_tag('question_response2', 'question_2', (@shipping_detail.question_response.question_2 == "True" ? false : true), :disabled => true) %> No
			</p>
		<% end %>

		<% if @shipping_detail.product.try(:question_3_is_enabled) %>
			<p>
				<b><%= @shipping_detail.product.question_3_name %> </b> <br/>
				<%= radio_button_tag('question_response3', 'question_3', (@shipping_detail.question_response.question_3 == "1" ? true : false), :disabled => true) %> Poor <br/>
				<%= radio_button_tag('question_response3', 'question_3', (@shipping_detail.question_response.question_3 == "2" ? true : false), :disabled => true) %> Average <br/>
				<%= radio_button_tag('question_response3', 'question_3', (@shipping_detail.question_response.question_3 == "3" ? true : false), :disabled => true) %> Good <br/>
				<%= radio_button_tag('question_response3', 'question_3', (@shipping_detail.question_response.question_3 == "4" ? true : false), :disabled => true) %> Excellent <br/>
			</p>
		<% end %>

		<% if @shipping_detail.product.try(:question_4_is_enabled) %>
			<% unless @shipping_detail.question_response.question_4.nil? %>
			<p>
				<b><%= @shipping_detail.product.question_4_name %> </b> <br/>
				<% @shipping_detail.product.question_options.each do |question_option| %>						
						<%= check_box_tag "question_response[question_4][]", question_option.id, (@shipping_detail.question_response.question_4.split(", ").include?(question_option.id.to_s) ? true : false), :disabled => true %> <%= question_option.name %> <br/>
				<% end %>
			</p>
			<% end %>
		<% end %>
			
	</div>
	<div class="customer-details">
		<p>
		  <b>Name:</b>
		  <%= @shipping_detail.first_name %> <%= @shipping_detail.last_name %>
		</p>
		
		<p>
		  <b>Email:</b>
		  <%= @shipping_detail.email %>
		</p>
		
		<p>
		  <b>Phone:</b>
		  <%= @shipping_detail.phone %>
		</p>
		
		<p>
		  <b>Address:</b>
		  <%= @shipping_detail.address1 %>; <%= @shipping_detail.address2 %><br/>
		  <%= @shipping_detail.city %>, <%= @shipping_detail.state %> <%= @shipping_detail.zip %>
		</p>
			
		<p>
		  <b>Payment method:</b>
		  <%= @shipping_detail.payment_method.name %>
		</p>
		
		<% if @shipping_detail.payment_method.short_code == "paypal" %>
		<p>
		  <b>Paypal email:</b>
		  <%= @shipping_detail.paypal_email %>
		</p>
		<% end %>
		
		<p>
		  <b>Do you requires a box?</b>
		  <%= (@shipping_detail.requires_box ? "Yes" : "No" ) %>
		</p>
	</div>
	
		<p>Thank you for your order. It is being processed. If you require a box and label, it will ship out at the end of the current or next business day. If you want to ship it on your own, please send to: </p>

		<p>
			DEPSTAR.COM<br/>
			PO BOX 52604<br/>
			BOSTON, MA 02205-1490
		</p>

		<p>If you are sending more than one phone please include them in the same package, we will calculate the values and send a single combined payment for the entire order.</p>

		<p>Please print this email and include it with your shipment. If you do not have a printer simply hand write all your information (name, address, email, phone, offer price) so it is clearly readable.</p>

		<p>We recommend shipping via USPS (The Post Office) priority mail. The postage for a flat rate envelope is only $4.95 and will be the fastest, easiest and safest way to get your phone to Depstar. We also offer free pick up through the post master.</p>

		<p>If you have any questions please email us anytime at info@depstar.com  or "Live Chat" on our home page is available 8AM till 8PM, 7 Days a week.</p>

		<p>Thank you for your business and support.</p>

		<p>
			Depstar.com<br/>
			email: info@depstar.com
		</p>

  </body>
</html>